00:15:59,910 --> 00:16:01,230
is gaining more respect and support.

289
00:16:01,640 --> 00:16:03,150
Who knows when

290
00:16:04,320 --> 00:16:05,910
I'll have to hand my position

291
00:16:07,350 --> 00:16:09,030
as the Crown Prince over to him.

292
00:16:11,790 --> 00:16:13,470
What can I do for you?

293
00:16:14,200 --> 00:16:15,790
You are the head of the officials.

294
00:16:16,320 --> 00:16:17,200
Only by joining hands together

295
00:16:18,280 --> 00:16:20,080
can we stand a chance.

296
00:16:29,640 --> 00:16:31,520
Why are you still hesitating?

297
00:16:31,960 --> 00:16:32,960
Your son's death is definitely ordered

298
00:16:33,110 --> 00:16:34,320
by someone in the imperial palace.

299
00:16:34,710 --> 00:16:35,960
Only by joining hands with me

300
00:16:36,280 --> 00:16:37,320
can you figure out the truth,

301
00:16:37,320 --> 00:16:38,280
find the real murderer,

302
00:16:38,400 --> 00:16:40,320
and avenge your son's death.

303
00:16:41,150 --> 00:16:42,670
What if His Majesty is the one

304
00:16:44,960 --> 00:16:46,670
who ordered his death?

305
00:16:53,550 --> 00:16:54,440
I just said

306
00:16:55,550 --> 00:16:59,230
you could avenge your son's death.

307
00:17:05,070 --> 00:17:09,110
No word should be left concerning our alliance.

308
00:17:09,590 --> 00:17:10,430
Of course.

309
00:17:10,950 --> 00:17:12,710
It's OK as long as we reach consensus in heart.

310
00:17:17,190 --> 00:17:18,310
Why do you

311
00:17:19,110 --> 00:17:20,520
ask Fan Xian over specially?

312
00:17:21,000 --> 00:17:22,800
Prime Minister, he's the one

313
00:17:24,040 --> 00:17:25,000
we should fully support in future.

314
00:17:25,470 --> 00:17:26,520
Your Highness, you mean...

315
00:17:29,040 --> 00:17:29,950
As to our war against Beiqi,

316
00:17:30,230 --> 00:17:31,760
we've already captured one prefecture.

317
00:17:32,040 --> 00:17:33,430
The two sides called a truce in the
frontline the day before yesterday.

318
00:17:33,800 --> 00:17:34,760
The Beiqi mission

319
00:17:35,040 --> 00:17:36,590
are on their way to the capital city.

320
00:17:37,070 --> 00:17:38,000
Why am I related?

321
00:17:38,350 --> 00:17:39,310
This war is started

322
00:17:39,560 --> 00:17:41,880
by your investigation on Si Lili.

323
00:17:42,350 --> 00:17:43,160
That is to say,

324
00:17:43,430 --> 00:17:44,760
you've owned the top prize.

325
00:17:46,590 --> 00:17:48,000
We may have disputes,

326
00:17:48,640 --> 00:17:49,760
but we've never born

327
00:17:49,880 --> 00:17:51,110
a deep grudge against each other.

328
00:17:51,830 --> 00:17:54,040
You're talented, and I cherish talents.

329
00:17:55,070 --> 00:17:56,230
Why not join me?

330
00:17:58,110 --> 00:18:01,000
The Neiku will be handed over to you eventually,

331
00:18:01,350 --> 00:18:02,590
and I can let you have it.

332
00:18:03,040 --> 00:18:03,710
From today on,

333
00:18:03,950 --> 00:18:05,830
the Prime Minister and I

334
00:18:06,560 --> 00:18:08,350
will both be your support.

335
00:18:08,470 --> 00:18:09,800
We'll promise you a brilliant future.

336
00:18:19,710 --> 00:18:20,950
Think it over.

337
00:18:21,230 --> 00:18:22,590
We are still young.

338
00:18:22,800 --> 00:18:23,710
When I ascend the throne,

339
00:18:24,310 --> 00:18:25,950
we might make a much-told story
of the emperor and his subject

340
00:18:25,950 --> 00:18:28,950
fighting together from the start to the end.

341
00:18:33,950 --> 00:18:35,710
Be quiet outside!

342
00:18:39,520 --> 00:18:41,190
They have no rules!

343
00:18:41,430 --> 00:18:42,880
What on earth is happening outside?!

344
00:19:07,400 --> 00:19:08,520
Your men are here to rescue you.

345
00:19:08,520 --> 00:19:09,640
Impossible!

346
00:19:10,110 --> 00:19:10,920
What happened?

347
00:19:11,470 --> 00:19:12,350
Your Highness, please stay inside.

348
00:19:12,760 --> 00:19:14,110
The guards outside were slaughtered brutally.

349
00:19:14,470 --> 00:19:16,280
They must be killed by martial arts masters.

350
00:19:23,160 --> 00:19:23,830
Where are you going?

351
00:19:24,520 --> 00:19:25,350
Go out and see what's going on.

352
00:19:25,400 --> 00:19:26,070
It's dangerous.

353
00:19:26,640 --> 00:19:27,800
I'm the only one here who can practice martial arts.

354
00:19:28,280 --> 00:19:29,430
Or shall we let His Highness go out?

355
00:20:32,680 --> 00:20:33,520
Xie Bi'an.

356
00:20:34,040 --> 00:20:36,070
I heard that you are endowed with civil and martial virtues.

357
00:20:36,470 --> 00:20:37,880
Maybe we should compete with other swords.

358
00:20:39,640 --> 00:20:40,560
Don't blame him.

359
00:20:49,350 --> 00:20:50,760
Xie Bi'an is born with a poker face.

360
00:20:51,350 --> 00:20:52,710
He never said anything nice to me.

361
00:20:54,070 --> 00:20:54,830
I didn't expect that

362
00:20:56,160 --> 00:20:57,000
you would come.

363
00:20:57,160 --> 00:20:58,280
Neither do I.

364
00:21:05,350 --> 00:21:07,000
Don't listen to that one inside.

365
00:21:07,280 --> 00:21:08,920
He's always a persuasive talker.

366
00:21:09,350 --> 00:21:10,470
I didn't hear anything.

367
00:21:12,310 --> 00:21:13,190
Let's go inside.

368
00:21:18,430 --> 00:21:19,880
It's slippery. Slow down.

369
00:21:28,040 --> 00:21:29,470
Sorry for coming late.

370
00:21:29,640 --> 00:21:31,470
Your Highness, please forgive me.

371
00:21:31,880 --> 00:21:33,310
Why are you here?

372
00:21:36,000 --> 00:21:37,590
I was burning with anxiety

373
00:21:37,760 --> 00:21:38,710
after hearing that Your Highness was abducted,

374
00:21:38,920 --> 00:21:40,760
so I took Xie Bi'an with me to rescue you.

375
00:21:41,160 --> 00:21:42,710
But don't worry, Your Highness.

376
00:21:42,760 --> 00:21:44,110
The bandits outside

377
00:21:44,350 --> 00:21:47,430
were all killed by Xie Bi'an.

378
00:21:52,830 --> 00:21:54,350
Prime Minister, are you also here to rescue His Highness?

379
00:21:55,310 --> 00:21:56,160
I just passed by.

380
00:21:56,950 --> 00:21:58,230
Do you know the bandits outside?

381
00:21:59,470 --> 00:22:00,470
I've never met them.

382
00:22:00,800 --> 00:22:01,640
Then I'm relieved.

383
00:22:01,950 --> 00:22:03,040
I was worried that

384
00:22:03,040 --> 00:22:04,110
reckless as Xie Bi'an is,

385
00:22:04,520 --> 00:22:05,920
he might hurt our men.

386
00:22:07,470 --> 00:22:09,160
Your Highness, you're so kind.

387
00:22:09,520 --> 00:22:10,950
How admirable!

388
00:22:11,680 --> 00:22:12,400
I'm so flattered.

389
00:22:13,830 --> 00:22:15,830
Now that the Crown Prince is safe,

390
00:22:16,560 --> 00:22:19,830
I'll leave first.

391
00:22:35,950 --> 00:22:37,280
Your sword is nice.

392
00:22:37,590 --> 00:22:38,430
How much is it?

393
00:22:43,520 --> 00:22:44,230
Let's go.

394
00:22:44,230 --> 00:22:44,880
OK.

395
00:22:46,800 --> 00:22:47,560
Nice sword.

396
00:22:55,400 --> 00:22:56,920
You're really watching me closely all the time!

397
00:22:59,590 --> 00:23:01,350
Your Highness, you're the Crown Prince

398
00:23:01,880 --> 00:23:02,920
and my brother as well.

399
00:23:03,350 --> 00:23:04,470
How can I not try my best

400
00:23:04,880 --> 00:23:06,430
to protect your safety?

401
00:23:06,430 --> 00:23:09,000
What a nice brother!

402
00:23:10,040 --> 00:23:12,000
I'm so touched!

403
00:23:12,230 --> 00:23:13,230
It's my duty.

404
00:23:14,560 --> 00:23:15,950
But Your Highness, do feel relieved.

405
00:23:16,520 --> 00:23:17,560
I've been keeping an eye on

406
00:23:18,000 --> 00:23:18,760
the capital city

407
00:23:18,760 --> 00:23:20,110
on your behalf.

408
00:23:20,470 --> 00:23:22,070
Any sign of disturbance

409
00:23:22,560 --> 00:23:23,760
won't escape my eyes.

410
00:23:27,830 --> 00:23:29,800
Then I'm relieved.

411
00:23:30,280 --> 00:23:31,190
May I escort Your Highness

412
00:23:31,190 --> 00:23:31,880
back to the Eastern Palace?

413
00:23:33,070 --> 00:23:34,310
You're most welcome.

414
00:23:51,040 --> 00:23:52,110
Why is the Second Prince coming so fast?

415
00:23:53,400 --> 00:23:54,310
They are

416
00:23:54,590 --> 00:23:56,070
really competing fiercely.

417
00:23:56,640 --> 00:23:58,230
Uncle, will you really ally with the Crown Prince?

418
00:23:58,400 --> 00:23:59,350
I was just saying.

419
00:24:00,280 --> 00:24:02,000
It's better not to offend either of them.

420
00:24:02,760 --> 00:24:04,190
Now the imperial court is in chaos.

421
00:24:04,760 --> 00:24:06,230
We can take this chance

422
00:24:06,430 --> 00:24:07,800
and get you a higher rank.

423
00:24:11,400 --> 00:24:12,760
This time, I really mean it.

424
00:24:13,070 --> 00:24:14,110
No more suspicions.

425
00:24:15,230 --> 00:24:16,070
I just don't know

426
00:24:16,680 --> 00:24:18,070
how much time I've left.

427
00:24:19,400 --> 00:24:20,310
But Uncle,

428
00:24:20,310 --> 00:24:21,190
you look healthy.

429
00:24:22,800 --> 00:24:23,950
I won't die for the moment.

430
00:24:25,000 --> 00:24:26,640
I mean how long can I

431
00:24:27,520 --> 00:24:28,880
keep my position?

432
00:24:31,040 --> 00:24:33,800
Actually, being an official is like being a man.

433
00:24:34,040 --> 00:24:36,190
It's like standing on the top of a mountain.

434
00:24:36,880 --> 00:24:39,520
The further you move forward,
the more cautious you should be.

435
00:24:39,920 --> 00:24:43,070
Otherwise, you'll be doomed eternally.

436
00:24:46,280 --> 00:24:47,230
Can I retreat on my own?

437
00:24:49,040 --> 00:24:52,310
You can't once you go up.

438
00:24:53,040 --> 00:24:53,920
Prime Minister.

439
00:24:57,880 --> 00:24:58,710
They were all killed.

440
00:24:59,640 --> 00:25:00,830
No one was left alive.

441
00:25:01,560 --> 00:25:03,070
All their families are outside the capital city.

442
00:25:04,470 --> 00:25:05,400
Don't bury them.

443
00:25:06,470 --> 00:25:08,400
We can't afford to take any risk.

444
00:25:09,000 --> 00:25:10,470
Help their families settle down well.

445
00:25:16,880 --> 00:25:18,280
Don't blame me for being merciless.

446
00:25:19,230 --> 00:25:22,400
If I'm softhearted, I might endanger myself.

447
00:25:23,310 --> 00:25:24,680
Well, enough for today.

448
00:25:24,950 --> 00:25:26,430
You've been through a lot today.

449
00:25:27,520 --> 00:25:28,430
Go back early.

450
00:26:22,230 --> 00:26:23,040
Uncle.

451
00:26:24,400 --> 00:26:25,230
You're here.

452
00:26:25,430 --> 00:26:26,520
You're upset.

453
00:26:27,430 --> 00:26:29,190
So many things happened today.

454
00:26:30,000 --> 00:26:31,280
The powerful arrow of Yan Xiaoyi.

455
00:26:31,590 --> 00:26:32,830
The brutality of Xie Bi'an.

456
00:26:33,230 --> 00:26:34,920
Running into His Majesty in the Taiping Residence.

457
00:26:35,680 --> 00:26:36,950
Removing Lin Ruofu's suspicion

458
00:26:36,950 --> 00:26:38,070
of me completely.

459
00:26:38,470 --> 00:26:39,070
Also,

460
00:26:39,710 --> 00:26:40,830
the Second Prince and the Crown Prince

461
00:26:40,880 --> 00:26:41,830
are standing in sharp opposition to each other.

462
00:26:42,110 --> 00:26:43,640
Which one upsets you?

463
00:26:47,190 --> 00:26:48,640
The Crown Prince is trying to draw me over to his side.

464
00:26:49,350 --> 00:26:50,640
We may have disputes,

465
00:26:50,640 --> 00:26:52,350
but we've never born a deep grudge against each other.

466
00:26:53,110 --> 00:26:55,350
You're talented, and I cherish talents.

467
00:26:56,710 --> 00:26:58,000
Why not join me?

468
00:26:59,350 --> 00:27:00,350
What's wrong?

469
00:27:01,880 --> 00:27:02,920
We used to believe that

470
00:27:03,470 --> 00:27:05,190
Lin Gong planned the Niulan Street assassination

471
00:27:05,520 --> 00:27:06,830
at the command of the Crown Prince.

472
00:27:07,430 --> 00:27:08,350
But now

473
00:27:09,310 --> 00:27:10,560
he actually said he had never

474
00:27:10,560 --> 00:27:11,680
born a deep grudge against me.

475
00:27:12,040 --> 00:27:13,520
Maybe he believes you don't know the truth.

476
00:27:14,640 --> 00:27:15,710
The news that Lin Gong tried to assassinate me

477
00:27:15,710 --> 00:27:16,800
has spread all over the capital city.

478
00:27:18,470 --> 00:27:19,800
If the Crown Prince is really behind it,

479
00:27:21,190 --> 00:27:22,230
he won't lay down his guard against me

480
00:27:22,310 --> 00:27:23,310
so easily.

481
00:27:23,590 --> 00:27:24,950
Maybe he doesn't mean it.

482
00:27:25,160 --> 00:27:26,230
He asked to see me specially.

483
00:27:26,920 --> 00:27:27,950
Judged from his look,

484
00:27:28,520 --> 00:27:29,590
he really wants to draw me over to his side.

485
00:27:30,070 --> 00:27:30,830
So?

486
00:27:31,230 --> 00:27:32,800
So I've been wondering

487
00:27:33,950 --> 00:27:35,070
what if

488
00:27:35,070 --> 00:27:36,190
the Crown Prince

489
00:27:38,590 --> 00:27:39,560
didn't give the order.

490
00:27:40,470 --> 00:27:41,350
Then who would it be?

491
00:27:43,520 --> 00:27:45,560
I also want to know.

492
00:27:50,830 --> 00:27:51,710
If you can't figure it out now,

493
00:27:53,470 --> 00:27:54,590
just think about it some other day.

494
00:27:59,590 --> 00:28:00,110
Sometimes,

495
00:28:00,110 --> 00:28:01,760
I do envy your character.

496
00:28:02,590 --> 00:28:03,400
It doesn't suit you.

497
00:28:03,920 --> 00:28:05,040
Indeed!

498
00:28:05,640 --> 00:28:06,560
Have you found the key?

499
00:28:06,760 --> 00:28:07,430
No.

500
00:28:08,880 --> 00:28:09,830
Then it must be kept in the imperial palace.

501
00:28:10,190 --> 00:28:11,760
Most of your mom's things

502
00:28:12,280 --> 00:28:13,830
are kept by that old lady.

503
00:28:15,280 --> 00:28:16,310
Which old lady?

504
00:28:19,590 --> 00:28:20,110
The Empress Dowager.

505
00:28:23,800 --> 00:28:24,760
Once we confirm its location,

506
00:28:25,640 --> 00:28:26,640
the rest is easy.

507
00:28:27,920 --> 00:28:28,950
The only problem

508
00:28:29,350 --> 00:28:30,830
is that Great Master Hong Sixiang in the imperial palace.

509
00:28:31,920 --> 00:28:33,350
Is he a guard beside His Majesty?

510
00:28:33,400 --> 00:28:34,640
He guards right beside the Empress Dowager.

511
00:28:39,000 --> 00:28:39,680
Nothing is worse

512
00:28:39,680 --> 00:28:41,110
than that.

513
00:29:01,760 --> 00:29:02,830
The mosquito bites

514
00:29:02,920 --> 00:29:04,310
are really itchy.

515
00:29:04,430 --> 00:29:05,400
They sure are.

516
00:29:07,950 --> 00:29:08,950
Look, there's no mosquito

517
00:29:09,350 --> 00:29:10,640
around the Empress Dowager.

518
00:29:11,000 --> 00:29:12,000
Eunuch Hong is there.

519
00:29:12,160 --> 00:29:13,190
How dare the mosquitoes go there?

520
00:29:16,400 --> 00:29:17,950
By then, we'll adopt our strategy today.

521
00:29:19,470 --> 00:29:20,190
What strategy?

522
00:29:20,400 --> 00:29:21,280
I will hold the Great Master,

523
00:29:21,760 --> 00:29:22,710
and you will go inside to find the key.

524
00:29:23,590 --> 00:29:24,280
Uncle.

525
00:29:24,800 --> 00:29:26,190
Besides the Great Master,

526
00:29:26,520 --> 00:29:27,590
Yan Xiaoyi, the Director of Imperial Guards,

527
00:29:27,920 --> 00:29:28,950
also guards the imperial palace

528
00:29:29,160 --> 00:29:29,920
all the year round.

529
00:29:40,680 --> 00:29:41,640
Just go and find the key.

530
00:29:42,830 --> 00:29:43,920
You really trust me so much?

531
00:29:44,040 --> 00:29:45,560
In this world, I can trust no one

532
00:29:46,160 --> 00:29:47,190
but you.

533
00:29:53,880 --> 00:29:54,680
Uncle,

534
00:29:57,070 --> 00:29:59,710
have you ever felt lonely?

535
00:30:00,520 --> 00:30:01,310
No.

536
00:30:01,920 --> 00:30:03,000
Even after my mom

537
00:30:03,680 --> 00:30:04,590
passed away?

538
00:30:06,710 --> 00:30:07,560
Right.

539
00:30:11,400 --> 00:30:12,400
When you get old,

540
00:30:13,760 --> 00:30:14,680
I'll be there for you.

541
00:30:16,160 --> 00:30:17,310
I probably won't get old.

542
00:30:19,590 --> 00:30:20,830
Then when I get old,

543
00:30:21,280 --> 00:30:22,280
you should be there for me.

544
00:30:23,230 --> 00:30:24,110
Only if you still feel like that

545
00:30:24,710 --> 00:30:25,640
by then.

546
00:30:26,520 --> 00:30:27,430
OK.

547
00:30:29,280 --> 00:30:30,190
Speaking of my life,

548
00:30:31,470 --> 00:30:32,350
you're the first man I saw

549
00:30:32,350 --> 00:30:33,830
since I could remember.

550
00:30:34,400 --> 00:30:35,160
Perhaps,

551
00:30:36,590 --> 00:30:37,950
you'll also be the last man I see

552
00:30:38,470 --> 00:30:39,230
in future.

553
00:30:41,640 --> 00:30:42,430
Maybe you're still young

554
00:30:42,430 --> 00:30:43,590
even by then.

555
00:30:48,950 --> 00:30:49,830
Shouldn't we discuss about

556
00:30:49,830 --> 00:30:50,800
finding the key in the imperial palace?

557
00:30:54,880 --> 00:30:55,590
Right.

558
00:30:56,520 --> 00:30:57,280
Go on.

559
00:31:05,190 --> 00:31:06,190
The problem is

560
00:31:06,430 --> 00:31:07,800
do you know where the Empress Dowager lives.

561
00:31:08,310 --> 00:31:09,000
No, I don't.

562
00:31:09,640 --> 00:31:10,230
Well then.

563
00:31:10,560 --> 00:31:11,950
You should find a chance to go to the imperial palace

564
00:31:11,950 --> 00:31:13,000
to figure out the route.

565
00:31:14,430 --> 00:31:15,280
What a coincidence!

566
00:31:15,680 --> 00:31:17,760
I'm going to the imperial palace tomorrow.

567
00:31:18,160 --> 00:31:18,800
How is that?

568
00:31:19,110 --> 00:31:20,590
Good. Remember to figure out the route.

569
00:31:22,110 --> 00:31:23,190
Isn't there anything in the world

570
00:31:23,190 --> 00:31:24,160
that can surprise you?

571
00:31:24,680 --> 00:31:25,350
No.

572
00:31:25,950 --> 00:31:28,190
Well, good for you.

573
00:31:29,520 --> 00:31:30,830
No words can express

574
00:31:30,830 --> 00:31:31,880
my admiration for you.

575
00:31:33,040 --> 00:31:33,760
Uncle.

576
00:31:34,230 --> 00:31:34,950
Do you find the climate especially dry

577
00:31:34,950 --> 00:31:36,400
