685
00:38:18,710 --> 00:38:19,520
the story.

686
00:38:21,150 --> 00:38:22,430
Because among the boundless crowd,

687
00:38:22,430 --> 00:38:23,470
we are

688
00:38:24,760 --> 00:38:25,470
so lucky

689
00:38:25,470 --> 00:38:26,870
to meet each other.

690
00:38:31,000 --> 00:38:32,520
You don't want us to miss each other.

691
00:38:37,320 --> 00:38:38,040
We won't

692
00:38:39,150 --> 00:38:40,840
miss each other for sure.

693
00:39:05,150 --> 00:39:06,600
How about a hug before I leave?

694
00:39:52,740 --> 00:39:56,100
=Fan mansion=

695
00:40:15,600 --> 00:40:18,040
We've received an imperial decree to
summon you into the imperial palace.

696
00:40:20,520 --> 00:40:21,910
Summon who?

697
00:40:23,190 --> 00:40:24,150
This time,

698
00:40:24,710 --> 00:40:26,840
