705
00:40:41,870 --> 00:40:42,670
I'd love to.

706
00:40:48,520 --> 00:40:49,320
Fine then.

707
00:40:51,190 --> 00:40:52,150
Me, too.

708
00:40:59,560 --> 00:41:00,520
No, I won't go.

709
00:41:00,520 --> 00:41:02,000
