729
00:41:45,600 --> 00:41:47,150
The word Imperial doesn't go with Danbo.
(Danbo means indifferent to fame and fortune in Chinese.)

730
00:41:47,470 --> 00:41:48,320
Then we can change the name.

731
00:41:48,560 --> 00:41:49,390
We open the bookstore

732
00:41:49,390 --> 00:41:50,630
to make money.

733
00:41:51,080 --> 00:41:51,910
In my opinion,

734
00:41:52,280 --> 00:41:53,280
