741
00:42:25,150 --> 00:42:27,190
Madam, you're gorgeous.

742
00:42:28,320 --> 00:42:29,950
Eunuch, I'm so flattered.

743
00:42:30,470 --> 00:42:31,320
I wonder

744
00:42:31,320 --> 00:42:32,870
